					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="display:none"><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/nav%3Aside/styleFrame.html?.side-block%20.heading%7Bcolor%3A%23ededed%3Bfont-family%3A'%E9%BB%91%E4%BD%93'%2Csans-serif%3Bfont-size%3A0.94rem%3Bborder-bottom%3Asolid%201px%20%23ededed%3B%7D.side-block%7Bborder%3Atransparent%3Bborder-radius%3A0%3Bbox-shadow%3Anone%3Bbackground-color%3A%2321252e%3B%7D.side-block%20.menu-item%20%3E%20.image%7Bdisplay%3Anone%3B%7D.side-block%20div.menu-item%20a%7Bcolor%3A%23cea0ff%3Btransition%3Acolor%200.15s%20linear%3B%7D.side-block%20div.menu-item%20a%3Ahover%7Bcolor%3A%23ffffff%3Btext-decoration%3Anone%3Bbackground-color%3A%23cea0ff%3B%7D" name="styleFrame"></iframe></div> <div style="display:none"><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/nav%3Aside/styleFrame.html?.side-block%20.heading%7Bcolor%3A%23ededed%3Bfont-family%3A'%E9%BB%91%E4%BD%93'%2Csans-serif%3Bfont-size%3A0.94rem%3Bborder-bottom%3Asolid%201px%20%23ededed%3B%7D.side-block%7Bborder%3Atransparent%3Bborder-radius%3A0%3Bbox-shadow%3Anone%3Bbackground-color%3A%2321252e%3B%7D.side-block%20.menu-item%20%3E%20.image%7Bdisplay%3Anone%3B%7D.side-block%20div.menu-item%20a%7Bcolor%3A%231eb5e8%3Btransition%3Acolor%200.15s%20linear%3B%7D.side-block%20div.menu-item%20a%3Ahover%7Bcolor%3A%23ffffff%3Btext-decoration%3Anone%3Bbackground-color%3A%231eb5e8%3B%7D" name="styleFrame"></iframe></div> <div class="creditRate"> <div class="creditButtonStandalone"> <p><a class="fa fa-info" href="#u-credit-view"></a></p> </div> </div> <div style="clear:both;"></div> <div id="u-credit-view"> <div class="fader"> <p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/1" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="" style=""></iframe></p> </div> <div class="modalcontainer"> <div class="modalbox"> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h2><span>著作信息</span></h2> </div> <hr /> <div class="credit first"> <p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p> <p>组件页：<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/component:sybadge">http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/component:sybadge</a></p> <p>基金会炫酷成就徽章，作者：<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3781861&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610198999" alt="EstrellaYoshte" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3781861)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" >EstrellaYoshte</a></span></p> </div> <hr /> <div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;"> <p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <p>借用<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rjb-r" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610198999" alt="RJB_R" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rjb-r" >RJB_R</a></span>的一句话：</p> <blockquote> <p><em>这只是一个寻乐子的页面，来提供些徽章给那些想要在作者页列出他们自己所取得的成就的人。</em></p> </blockquote> <p>这个页面的主要目的就是以整洁的外观来展示用户的成就，并且鼓励社区参与制作。以下所有成就目的都已尽可能与自主评分无关。</p> <p>由于我无法强制定下获得成就的需求，因此这个仅基于荣誉制度，我也希望每个人都能尽力而为地去奋斗，还有记得快乐就好！</p> <hr /> <div class="anchor"> <div class="sidebox" style="padding: 10px;"> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h3><span>已解锁成就</span></h3> <h5><span>（共<span style="color: #cea0ff">16</span>个）</span></h5> </div> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/rachud-s-personnel-file">Rachud</a> - 3<br /> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/xolo">xOLowithSinnine</a> - 3<br /> <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/gyakkou-s-workbench">Backlight SH</a> - 1</p> </div> </div> <div class="casercontainer"> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>TSF</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/tsf.png" width="160px" alt="tsf.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>迈出十步</span></h1> <hr /> <p>发布10个页面<br /> （要是你想知道的话，迭代页是不算数的。）</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>MWW</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/mww.png" width="160px" alt="mww.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>世界博士</span></h1> <hr /> <p>你的某篇作品被翻译成5种或以上的语言，<strong>或</strong>你已将6篇作品翻译成另一种语言。</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>CCC</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/ccc.png" width="160px" alt="ccc.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>设定交叉中心</span></h1> <hr /> <p>撰写一篇包含3个（或以上）设定的文章。为达成该成就，允许使用故事系列或者有其他有专用中心页的合并设定。</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>SEK</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/sek.png" width="160px" alt="sek.png" class="image" /> <h1><span><span class="ruby">性感水槽<span class="rt">SEXTANK</span></span>倡议</span></h1> <hr /> <p>你已写过：<strong>S</strong>afe、<strong>E</strong>uclid、<strong>K</strong>eter、<strong>T</strong>haumiel、<span class="ruby">无效化<span class="rt"><strong>N</strong>eutralized</span></span>、<span class="ruby">已解明<span class="rt">E<strong>x</strong>plained</span></span> + <span class="ruby">其它<span class="rt"><strong>A</strong>nother</span></span>机密分级。<br /> （完全缺少项目等级的不算作机密。）</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>SCL</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/scl.png" width="160px" alt="scl.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>社交蝴蝶</span></h1> <hr /> <p>在讨论区留下20次详明的且有建设性的批判。<br /> 你可以自己决定哪些是详明且有建设性的。点子和草稿的批判也算数。</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>CLB</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/component:sybadge/clb.png" width="160px" alt="clb.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>感谢您的合作</span></h1> <hr /> <p>与至少7名其他作者合作。<br /> 可以是有7个不同的合著页或者一个有着7名合著者的合著页，或者介于两者之间的任何情况（你必须被记为合著者才有资格。）</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>DDA</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/dda.png" width="160px" alt="dda.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>双重双面间谍</span></h1> <hr /> <p>写4个或更多不同的GoI格式（至少要有一篇包含了四个GoI的文章。）</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>GSA</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/gsa.png" width="160px" alt="gsa.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>客串明星出场</span></h1> <hr /> <p>写一篇以某个由外语分部创作的SCP、GoI、角色或者其它主要元素为特色的文章（要是很隐晦的话还是个加分点！）</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>TLT</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/tlt.png" width="160px" alt="tlt.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>奇闻轶事</span></h1> <hr /> <p>发布10篇故事。部分较大的故事也算，只要它们是分开的页面。</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>TBE</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/tbe.png" width="160px" alt="tbe.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>团建练习</span></h1> <hr /> <p>写一篇以两个（或以上）从未合作过/甚至很少碰面的角色或GoI决定联手一次的文章。无论如何要是不包含基金会的话会是个加分点。</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>CHL</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/chl.png" width="160px" alt="chl.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>挑战者</span></h1> <hr /> <p>完成<a class="newpage" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/writing-challenge-list">写作挑战清单</a>中的至少三项挑战。</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>STR</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/str.png" width="160px" alt="str.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>大步向前</span></h1> <hr /> <p>发布50个页面。<br /> （迭代页还是不算数，哈。）</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>AWB</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/awb.png" width="160px" alt="awb.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>我们是坏人？</span></h1> <hr /> <p>写一篇基金会为明确敌对势力的文章。</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>CTS</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/cts.png" width="160px" alt="cts.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>百夫长</span></h1> <hr /> <p>发布100个页面。喔！<br /> （你真的很棒，知道吗？）</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>PBS</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/pbs.png" width="160px" alt="pbs.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>双站点游玩</span></h1> <hr /> <p>同时成为基金会与<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:start">被放逐者之图书馆</a>的作者。</p> </div> <div class="caser"> <div class="codecon"> <h5><span>SPA</span></h5> </div> <br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/spa.png" width="160px" alt="spa.png" class="image" /> <h1><span>学生参与奖</span></h1> <hr /> <p>全程参与两个由网站主办的研习会或研讨会。要是你用上在这其中学到的知识发布一篇文章会是个加分点！</p> </div> </div> <hr /> <p>若要在你的页面放入徽章，请添加如下内容：</p> <div class="darkbox" style="font-family: monospace;"> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[=]]</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;component:sybadge&#32;code=aaa]]</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;component:sybadge&#32;code=bbb]]</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/=]]</span></p> </div> <br /> 在<em>aaa</em>和<em>bbb</em>处填入显示于卡片左上角的三个字母的关键词，需与你选择的徽章对应（全小写）。 <div style="text-align: center;"><span class="tooltip"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/dark-achievement-badges"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/sek.png" style="background-color: var(--bgBadgeColor); padding: .66rem .7rem .4rem .5rem; border-radius: .6rem 2.5rem .6rem .6rem; margin: .3rem; border: solid 4px var(--borderColor);" width="64px" alt="sek.png" class="image" /></a><span class="tooltiptext"><span class="sek"> </span></span></span><span class="tooltip"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/dark-achievement-badges"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/component%3Asybadge/scl.png" style="background-color: var(--bgBadgeColor); padding: .66rem .7rem .4rem .5rem; border-radius: .6rem 2.5rem .6rem .6rem; margin: .3rem; border: solid 4px var(--borderColor);" width="64px" alt="scl.png" class="image" /></a><span class="tooltiptext"><span class="scl"> </span></span></span></div> <p>若要改变徽章边框与背景的颜色，填入以下代码：</p> <div class="darkbox" style="font-family: monospace;"> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[module&#32;CSS]]</span><br /> :root {<br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;--borderColor:&#32;（颜色）&#32;!important;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;--bgBadgeColor:&#32;（颜色）&#32;!important;</span><br /> }<br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/module]]</span></p> </div> <p>默认颜色分别为#CEA0FF和#21252E。</p> <hr /> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <h1><span>有要做一个的点子？</span></h1> <p>这个页面会继续更新新的成就。<br /> 如果你认为还有需要添加的，评论留言！我会尽我最大所能把它放进来的！</p> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hoah2333" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4915183&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610198999" alt="hoah2333" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4915183)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hoah2333" >hoah2333</a></span></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
