					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="display:none"><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/nav%3Aside/styleFrame.html?bhl" name="typeFrame"></iframe></div> <div class="info-container"> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <div> <p style="text-align: center;"><strong>SCP-4991</strong> - <em>所以世界是这么结束的。不是伴随着一声巨响，而是伴随着一篇垃圾帖。</em></p> <hr /> <p>你会变成它们的巢穴。</p> <hr /> <p style="text-align: center;"><strong>图片来源</strong></p> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <a href="https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/536/30699875944_6962e33cdf_b.jpg">https://c1.staticflickr.com/1/536/30699875944_6962e33cdf_b.jpg</a><br /> <a href="https://img.fireden.net/v/thumb/1446/05/1446058164129s.jpg">https://img.fireden.net/v/thumb/1446/05/1446058164129s.jpg</a><br /> <a href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/28/Plague_locust.jpg">https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/28/Plague_locust.jpg</a></p> <p>对不起，我不会内部编码</p> </div> <hr /> <div id="u-author_block"> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><span class="logical-link-wrap"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/westrinsauthorpage">westrinsauthorpage</a><span class="logical-link-internal logical-link-internal-false"><span class="logical-link-title logical-link-link-true"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/westrinsauthorpage">Westrin的人事档案</a></span><span class="logical-link-custom logical-link-link-true"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/westrinsauthorpage">▸ 该作者的更多作品 ◂</a></span></span><span class="logical-link-original logical-link-original-false"><span class="logical-link-appended">（<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/westrinsauthorpage">原文链接</a>）</span><span class="logical-link-title logical-link-link-true"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/westrinsauthorpage">westrinsauthorpage</a></span><span class="logical-link-custom logical-link-link-true"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/westrinsauthorpage">▸ 该作者的更多作品 ◂</a></span></span><span class="logical-link-mark-common logical-link-mark-mark-false" style="color: #009966"><sup><span class="fa fa-link"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></sup></span><span class="logical-link-mark-newpage logical-link-mark-mark-false" style="color: #F00"><sup><span class="fa fa-link"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></sup></span></span></p> </div> <hr /></div> <div class="translation_block"> <h1><span>其他语言</span></h1> </div> <div class="u-faq"> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/component:info-ayers">常见问题</a></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <p><a name="Class"></a></p> <div class="warning-box"> <div class="warning-box-container"> <div class="text-top"><span>根据监督员议会的命令</span></div> <div class="text-bottom"><span>以下文件描述一已无效化的异常。根据O5-1命令，禁止未经授权的访问。</span></div> </div> <div class="text-number"><span>4991</span></div> <div class="image-bg"></div> </div> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <div class="anom-bar-container item-4991 clear-4 无效化 {$secondary-class} 屁 刺猬索尼克的性 {$american} lang-cn"> <div class="anom-bar"> <div class="top-box"> <div class="top-left-box"><span class="item"><span class="lang-cn">项目编号：</span><span class="lang-tr">項目編號：</span></span><span class="number">4991</span></div> <div class="top-center-box"> <div class="bar-one"></div> <div class="bar-two"></div> <div class="bar-three"></div> <div class="bar-four"></div> <div class="bar-five"></div> <div class="bar-six"></div> </div> <div class="top-right-box"> <div class="level"><span class="lang-cn">等级</span><span class="lang-tr">等級</span>4</div> <div class="clearance"></div> </div> </div> <div class="bottom-box"> <div class="text-part"> <div class="main-class"> <div class="contain-class"> <div class="class-category"><span class="lang-cn">收容等级：</span><span class="lang-tr">收容等級：</span></div> <div class="class-text">无效化</div> </div> <div class="second-class"> <div class="class-category"><span class="lang-cn">次要等级：</span><span class="lang-tr">次要等級：</span></div> <div class="class-text">{$secondary-class}</div> </div> </div> <div class="disrupt-class"> <div class="class-category"><span class="lang-cn">扰动等级：</span><span class="lang-tr">擾動等級：</span></div> <div class="class-text">屁</div> </div> <div class="risk-class"> <div class="class-category"><span class="lang-cn">风险等级：</span><span class="lang-tr">風險等級：</span></div> <div class="class-text">刺猬索尼克的性</div> </div> </div> <div class="diamond-part"> <div class="danger-diamond"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/classification-committee-memo">备忘录链接</a><br /> <div class="arrows"></div> <div class="octagon"></div> <div class="quadrants"> <div class="top-quad"></div> <div class="right-quad"></div> <div class="left-quad"></div> <div class="bottom-quad"></div> </div> <div class="top-icon"></div> <div class="right-icon"></div> <div class="left-icon"></div> <div class="bottom-icon"></div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <p><strong>特殊收容措施：</strong>被SCP-4991感染过的所有社交网站中关于此事故的记录已被完全清除。关于ARG（侵入式虚拟现实游戏）的故事已被散布以掩盖任何该事故可能残留的证据。</p> <p><strong>描述：</strong>SCP-4991发生于2016年4月7日至4月9日之间的一段时间。在此期间，各大主流社交媒体，如4chan，Reddit，Tumblr，及Twitter等发布了提及现实中不存在的事件的帖子。用户经历了阻止他们发帖的故障。此事件中被发布的所有帖子均来自已存在的账户。</p> <p>所有异常活动在SCP-4991出现两天后停止，用户也能够正常使用网站。在O5议会以11-1通过将SCP-4991重新分类为已无效化的决定后，当前的收容措施被创建。在此事故后，目前为止并未检测到类似SCP-4991的异常活动。</p> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><strong>附录4991.1</strong></p> </div> <hr /> <p>在基金会特工获得关于绝大多数社交媒体无法被访问及用户报告账户中出现他们并未发布的帖子的警告后，SCP-4991于4月7日早上被发现。在联合委员会<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-812920-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup>的命令下，受影响的全部网站被暂时关闭，且一例病毒性K级记忆消除程序在SCP-4991消失后被发布。</p> <p>以下为SCP-4991期间被发布帖子的一部分例子。</p> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼&nbsp;Twitter记录</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▲&nbsp;它们将要演化</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <div style="background: url(/local--files/experimental-2-no-tocar/archivelogobackground.png) center top no-repeat ; float: center; border: grey 4px; width: 370px; padding: 5px; margin: 10px; background-color: light gray; box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.1);"> <p><span style="float:left; margin-left:5px; margin-top:12px; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px 10px;"><br /></span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: grey">Donald J. Trump @realDonaldTrump<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-812920-2" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >2</a></sup></span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: black">摩尔已退出了协议。这几乎像是在“世界即将结束”的时候他开始变得有些不安似的。难道地球对你来说还不够好吗？</span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <ul> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">转推</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">19K</span></span></li> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">喜欢</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">105K</span></span></li> </ul> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">2016年4月7日 - 美国，纽约</span></span></p> </div> <div style="background: url(/local--files/experimental-2-no-tocar/archivelogobackground.png) center top no-repeat ; float: center; border: grey 4px; width: 370px; padding: 5px; margin: 10px; background-color: light gray; box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.1);"> <p><span style="float:left; margin-left:5px; margin-top:12px; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px 10px;"><br /></span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: grey">鹿学院<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-812920-3" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >3</a></sup></span></span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: grey">@deercollege</span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: black">我们在此建议当地鹿学院学生们暂停使用昆虫秘术。另外，通向仙灵地区的入口目前已被关闭已进行维护。</span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <ul> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">转推</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">11</span></span></li> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">喜欢</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">93</span></span></li> </ul> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">2016年4月7日 - 三波特兰</span></span></p> </div> <div style="background: url(/local--files/experimental-2-no-tocar/archivelogobackground.png) center top no-repeat ; float: center; border: grey 4px; width: 370px; padding: 5px; margin: 10px; background-color: light gray; box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.1);"> <p><span style="float:left; margin-left:5px; margin-top:12px; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px 10px;"><br /></span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: grey">世界卫生部 @healthministryearth<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-812920-4" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >4</a></sup></span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: black">这是一则对所有北美居民的警告，请不要出门。如果你在户外呼吸过，请打给毒物控制。</span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <ul> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">转推</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">259</span></span></li> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">喜欢</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">1,273</span></span></li> </ul> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">2016年4月7日 - 瑞典</span></span></p> </div> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <div style="background: url(/local--files/experimental-2-no-tocar/archivelogobackground.png) center top no-repeat ; float: center; border: grey 4px; width: 370px; padding: 5px; margin: 10px; background-color: light gray; box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.1);"> <p><span style="float:left; margin-left:5px; margin-top:12px; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px 10px;"><br /></span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: grey">Faeowynn Wilson<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-812920-5" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >5</a></sup></span></span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: grey">@FaeWWS</span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: black">看起来我们像是到了终点了。我希望所有人，在他们还能做到的时候，保证自己的安全。只要我还活着，我的私信信箱会保持开启，如果任何人需要聊一聊。</span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <ul> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">转推</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">22</span></span></li> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">喜欢</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">10K</span></span></li> </ul> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">2016年4月8日 - 美国，俄勒冈</span></span></p> </div> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <div style="background: url(/local--files/experimental-2-no-tocar/archivelogobackground.png) center top no-repeat ; float: center; border: grey 4px; width: 370px; padding: 5px; margin: 10px; background-color: light gray; box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.1);"> <p><span style="float:left; margin-left:5px; margin-top:12px; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px 10px;"><br /></span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: grey">방탄소년단<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-812920-6" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >6</a></sup></span></span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: grey">@BTS_twt</span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: black">숨을 못 쉬겠어<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-812920-7" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >7</a></sup></span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <ul> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">转推</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">756K</span></span></li> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">喜欢</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">2.1M</span></span></li> </ul> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">2016年4月8日 - 韩国</span></span></p> </div> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <div style="background: url(/local--files/experimental-2-no-tocar/archivelogobackground.png) center top no-repeat ; float: center; border: grey 4px; width: 370px; padding: 5px; margin: 10px; background-color: light gray; box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.1);"> <p><span style="float:left; margin-left:5px; margin-top:12px; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px 10px;"><br /></span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: grey">me an intellectual</span></span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: grey">@fanboy431</span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: black">我们就要这么忽视MC&amp;D<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-812920-8" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >8</a></sup>正把反昆虫掩体卖出他妈的四百万美金的事实吗？这种狗屎难道可以接受吗？</span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <ul> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">转推</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">0</span></span></li> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">喜欢</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">39</span></span></li> </ul> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">2016年4月8日 - 美国，纽约</span></span></p> </div> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <div style="background: url(/local--files/experimental-2-no-tocar/archivelogobackground.png) center top no-repeat ; float: center; border: grey 4px; width: 370px; padding: 5px; margin: 10px; background-color: light gray; box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.1);"> <p><span style="float:left; margin-left:5px; margin-top:12px; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 0px 10px;"><br /></span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: grey">TRAVIS SCOTT<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-812920-9" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >9</a></sup></span></span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: grey">@trvisXX</span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:1.5em;"><span style="color: black">这一切最终也是要在泪水中结束的</span></span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <ul> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">转推</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">15K</span></span></li> <li><span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">喜欢</span></span> <span style="font-size:1.1em;"><span style="color: purple">1.5M</span></span></li> </ul> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="font-size:.8em;"><span style="color: grey">2016年4月9日 - 美国，加州</span></span></p> </div> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼&nbsp;Reddit记录</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▲&nbsp;它们将要适应</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4991/image0.jpg" alt="image0.jpg" class="image" /><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span> <hr /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-4991/reddit_tres.png" alt="reddit_tres.png" class="image" /><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span> <hr /> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wr