						 <div style="display:none"><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/nav%3Aside/styleFrame.html?bhl" name="typeFrame"></iframe></div> <div class="info-container"> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <div> <p>哈，这是我的作者页。</p> <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.pexels.com/zh-cn/photo/1852482/">https://www.pexels.com/zh-cn/photo/1852482/</a></p> <hr /> <p>该作者的上一篇作品：SCP-CN-443。</p> </div> <hr /> <div id="u-author_block"> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><span class="logical-link-wrap"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/djpieplus-s-scps">http://www.scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/djpieplus-s-scps</a><span class="logical-link-internal logical-link-internal-false"><span class="logical-link-title logical-link-link-true"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/djpieplus-s-scps">http:www-scp-wiki-cn-wikidot-com-djpieplus-s-scps</a></span><span class="logical-link-custom logical-link-link-true"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/djpieplus-s-scps">▸ 该作者的更多作品 ◂</a></span></span><span class="logical-link-original logical-link-original-false"><span class="logical-link-appended">（<a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/http://www.scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/djpieplus-s-scps">原文链接</a>）</span><span class="logical-link-title logical-link-link-true"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/http://www.scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/djpieplus-s-scps">http://www.scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/djpieplus-s-scps</a></span><span class="logical-link-custom logical-link-link-true"><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/http://www.scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/djpieplus-s-scps">▸ 该作者的更多作品 ◂</a></span></span><span class="logical-link-mark-common logical-link-mark-mark-false" style="color: #009966"><sup><span class="fa fa-link"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></sup></span><span class="logical-link-mark-newpage logical-link-mark-mark-false" style="color: #F00"><sup><span class="fa fa-link"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&nbsp;</span></span></sup></span></span></p> </div> <hr /></div> <div class="translation_block"> <h1><span>其他语言</span></h1> </div> <div class="u-faq"> <p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p> <p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/component:info-ayers">常见问题</a></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <p><br /></p> <div class="right-align"> <div class="rate-box-with-sentiment-bar"> <div class="sentiment-bar"></div> </div> </div> <br /> <br /> <br /> <div id="wiki-tabview-cd00ecd3baa6d3c99a9a86c98d21d257" class="yui-navset"> <ul class="yui-nav"> <li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>作品</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>人事档案</em></a></li> </ul> <div class="yui-content"> <div id="wiki-tab-0-0"> <table class="heritage"> <tr> <td class="title">作品列表</td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1649">SCP-CN-1649</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2020.7.1</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>终将离去</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>看那边的柳树，能把你留下吗？</em></p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1849">SCP-CN-1849</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2020.7.14</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>最后的孤独</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>那是茫茫的雪。那是我最后的孤独。</em></p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-443">SCP-CN-443</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2020.8.23</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>管理者们</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>那些头骨&#8230;和那些古籍，是痴心与幻想吧？</em></p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/stairs">楼梯还在那儿</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2020.8.28</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>TALE</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>我走上一台台阶，却忘记了台阶的存在。那是无休止的憎恨。</em></p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/write-lastly">篇章</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2020.9.18</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>TALE</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>一本日记，让我翻开看看这些独白的篇章吧…</em></p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/dismiss">解散</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2020.10.1</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>TALE</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>网络差到这个地步了，帖子内容都显现不出来了啊。</em></p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1728">SCP-CN-1728</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2020.10.4</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>无力</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>我希望我的文字不再被世人所需要，如果真有需要的那一天，怕才是可悲的吧。</em></p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1729">SCP-CN-1729</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2020.10.10</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>替罪羊</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>我听到了窗外的警笛声&#8230;有点刺耳。</em></p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/dream-or-real">这是梦的一环</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2020.11.6</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>TALE</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>我叫特工芜铭，而那不过只是我做过的几千个梦中普普通通的一个。</em></p> <p><strong>2020万圣节主题征文参赛作品</strong></p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/death-of-candy">糖纸在Site-CN-90内飘落</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2020.11.27</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>TALE</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>昨日丢进垃圾桶的糖纸，又飘了出来。</em></p> <p><strong>活人入棺主题下作品</strong></p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1317">SCP-CN-1317</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2020.12.18</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>三█餐馆</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>我被穿透。</em></p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:falling-down-in-the-sea">下坠</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2021.1.1</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>图书馆</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>血。</em></p> </div> </td> </tr> <tr> <td class="label"> <p><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/old-friends-story">老李和老张的故事</a></p> <div class="date"> <p>2021.1.8</p> </div> </td> <td class="entry"> <div class="description"> <p>TALE</p> </div> <div class="snippet"> <p><em>现在，我成了你的星星。</em></p> <p><strong>五花八门主题下作品。</strong></p> </div> </td> </tr> </table> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+懒人版</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-关闭</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><br /> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Works</span>:</p> <div class="infobox"></div> <div class="sortbar {$sortbar}"></div> <div class="translation {$translation}"></div> <div class="collab-header" style="text-align: center;"> <hr /> <h2><span>更多页面</span></h2> <hr /></div> <hr /> <hr /> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Translations</span>:<br /></p> <div class="preview yesyes" style="height:7.7em;overflow:hidden;"> <p><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/rebranding">rebranding</a></strong><br /> <span class="ratingofrebranding {$rating}"><em>主站评分：</em>+<tt><strong>{$rating}</strong></tt></span><br /> <span class="collabnoteofrebranding {$note}">{$note}</span><br /> <em>等待翻译&#8230;</em></p> </div> <div class="preview yesyes" style="height:7.7em;overflow:hidden;"> <p><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/recorded">recorded</a></strong><br /> <span class="ratingofrecorded {$rating}"><em>主站评分：</em>+<tt><strong>{$rating}</strong></tt></span><br /> <span class="collabnoteofrecorded {$note}">{$note}</span><br /> <em>等待翻译&#8230;</em></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-1" style="display:none"> <p><em>本来说是攒五篇原创再发的，然后我实在憋不住了(</em></p> <hr /> <p><strong>姓名：</strong>Pieplus</p> <p><strong>性别：</strong>男</p> <p><strong>年龄：</strong>36岁<span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><em>不我只有20岁</em></span></p> <p><strong>职位：</strong>Site-CN-90主管；Site-CN-12地点异常部主管</p> <p><strong>所属部门：</strong>Site-CN-90指挥部；Site-CN-12地点异常部</p> <p><strong>工作年龄：</strong>十五年</p> <p><strong>人设外观：</strong>Pieplus主管身高1.90米，体重[数据删除]<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-333838-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup>kg。除此之外，他习惯穿着黑色的大衣以及斗篷，在脸上戴一个白色的小丑面具，这大概是他的个人癖好吧。据称，他的黑色大衣上曾有一大片红色印记，不过研究员们在平常的工作中没有见过。</p> <div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:225px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/djpieplus-s-scps/PIEPLUS.webp.jpg" title="Click and hold to enlarge." style="width:225px;" class="fillpg" alt="PIEPLUS.webp.jpg" /> <div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:225px;"> <p>Pieplus主管的照片，这很帅，不是吗？</p> </div> </div> <p><strong>简述：</strong>Pieplus，Site-CN-90的站点主管，兼任Site-CN-12的地点异常部主管，拥有巨量的关于地点异常的知识，性格严肃。他拥有大量机密文档的权限<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-333838-2" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >2</a></sup>。</p> <p>有研究员称，Pieplus主管与GEC，异学会等多个GOI均有私底下的联系，目前无法确认其真假。</p> <p>Pieplus主管有时会不知何故地掏出██先生<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-333838-3" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >3</a></sup>所著的《██》进行大声朗读，无论是半夜或者是激烈的战斗现场，现已知有超过████名研究员因此而向O5指挥部投诉。</p> <p>无论如何，那些投诉的研究员都因为“恶意骚扰O5议会”而被降为D级人员了，据悉他们参与了<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-3000">SCP-3000</a>的最新十轮投喂。</p> </div> </div> </div> <div style="font-family:微软细黑 !important;"> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">--&gt;讨论区动态</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&lt;--收起</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <div class="left_float"> <div style="padding:2px"> <h4><span>最热主题</span></h4> </div> </div> <div class="right_float"> <div style="padding:2px;"> <h4><span>最新主题</span></h4> </div> </div> <div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">--&gt;当月计分板</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&lt;--收起</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <div class="left_float"> <div style="background-color:#f0f0f0;padding:4%;margin: 5%;"> <p><span style="font-family:微软细黑">本月最高评分SCP</span></p> </div> <div style="background-color:#f0f0f0;padding:4%;margin: 5%;"> <p><span style="font-family:微软细黑">原创GoI格式或其他页面</span></p> </div> </div> <div class="right_float"> <div style="background-color:#f0f0f0;padding:4%;margin: 5%;"> <p><span style="font-family:微软细黑">本月最高评分故事</span></p> </div> <div style="background-color:#f0f0f0;padding:4%;margin: 5%;"> <p><span style="font-family:微软细黑">本月最高评分原创图书馆</span></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div> </div> <div style="background-color: transparent; padding-left: 7px;border-left: solid 5px #3399ff; border-radius: 0px 10px 10px 0px;"> <p><span style="font-size:120%;"><strong>Site-CN-90</strong></span></p> <p>成立于1900年，具体地点尚不明了，对外掩饰为私人图书馆。该站点致力于对地点异常进行研究，或是对异常气象、现象等无实体异常进行掩盖。负责项目包括<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1649">SCP-CN-1649</a>。</p> </div> <div style="background-color: transparent; padding-left: 7px;border-left: solid 5px #3399ff; border-radius: 0px 10px 10px 0px;"> <p><span style="font-size:120%;"><strong>Site-CN-12</strong></span></p> <p>建立于1953年7月10日，其为SCP基金会中国分部第一个尝试使用异常空间拓扑结构以及奇术建造的站点。由CN-O5议会下令建造，直属O5议会。站点内携带2枚500吨当量的核弹头。有涉及的项目包括<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-443">SCP-CN-443</a>。</p> </div> <a href="http://scpsandboxcn.wikidot.com/collab:12"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/local--files/djpieplus-s-scps/12.gif" alt="12.gif" class="image" /></a> <div style="border-bottom:2px solid #777; margin-bottom:1px;"></div> <div style="border-bottom:1px solid #777;"></div> <p><em>这是留言板吧？</em></p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+展开？</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-关上</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"></div> </div> </div> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djpieplus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6603529&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610199009" alt="djpieplus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6603529)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djpieplus" >djpieplus</a></span></p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">脚注</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-333838-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. 不能乱说，很毁我形象的。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-333838-2"><a href="javascript:;" >2</a>. 哈我当然知道你们这群兔崽子读者啥都能看，但是让我开心一下不行吗。</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-333838-3"><a href="javascript:;" >3</a>. Pieplus主管本人要求如此称呼他。</div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
